cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.IR

This paper covers a wide range of topics related to knowledge graphs, including representation learning, knowledge acquisition and completion, temporal knowledge graphs, and knowledge-aware applications. These topics are all closely related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as databases (cs.DB), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
